\newlabel{fig:forest_v_open_swe}{{5}{15}{A comparison of daily SWE in the open (observed by the NRCS snow pillow) and forest (observed by manual federal sampler measurements) against the SUMMA model (dashed gray and yellow lines, respectively)}{figure.5}{}}
